###### Description

Here you will find some sample responses you can
use as a reference to create your own.

---

###### Registering a single appliance

Validate specific appliance attributes:

```
{
    "validate": {
        "deviceInfo": {
            "applianceType": "washingMachine",
            "applianceID": "MY_APPLIANCE",
            "serialNumber": "ABCD-1234-EFGH-5678"

        }
    }
}
```

---

###### Registering multiple appliances

Validate more generic attributes, suitable
for every appliance being registered:

```
{
    "validate": {
        "deviceInfo": {
            "applianceType": "washingMachine",
            "manufacturer": "Swirlmore",
            "model": "wkw007ge",
            "fwVersion": "1.0.0"

        }
    }
}
```

---

